<p>Welcome to Fitzwilliam College JCR&#8217;s online room and housing ballot system. The system is under active development by the JCR Website Officer, Tom Benn, building on work by last year&#8217;s officer Charlie Jonas.</p>

<h3>Group Balloting</h3>
<p>This year, the ballot is being done in groups. For full information, see <a href="/guide">the JCR&#8217;s ballot guide</a>. To start registering your groups, go to <a href="/groups">the group balloting page</a>.</p>
